body: When I click the start / start button then nothing happens

replies.body: Most of the time that happens because your OS is thinking League is an unsafe program, so it shuts it down before it can launch all the way. Double check that you have all the right [**permissions**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) set up, but let me know if that doesn't help out!
Run it as administrator, that would do the trick
I've tried it before and it did not help
